635
01:01:31,821 --> 01:01:34,461
And this is gonna sound
really strange but...

636
01:01:35,191 --> 01:01:37,762
but I think I know why.

637
01:01:38,928 --> 01:01:41,169
I believe there's a
presence in that house.

638
01:01:42,265 --> 01:01:45,546
I wouldn't be surprised
if there's more than one.

639
01:01:47,537 --> 01:01:49,881
I found pictures of you and your sister.

640
01:01:51,040 --> 01:01:54,044
You found pictures?
You found my family photos?

641
01:01:54,277 --> 01:01:56,813
Yeah. I can bring them to you,
or send them, if you like.

642
01:01:56,913 --> 01:01:58,715
Please bring them.

643
01:01:58,815 --> 01:02:03,586
